This paper proposes a reinforcement learning approach to optimize data usage in machine learning models. The paper focuses on two tasks, machine translation and image classification, which are both related to natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
